---
interface Props {
  title: string;
  description: string;
}

const { title, description } = Astro.props;
const siteTitle = 'firel.cn';
const fullTitle = title === siteTitle ? title : `${title} - ${siteTitle}`;
---

<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="description" content={description} />
    <title>{fullTitle}</title>
    <link rel="canonical" href={new URL(Astro.url.pathname, Astro.site).href} />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="nav-header">
      <a href="/" class="site-name">firel.cn</a>
      <nav>
        <a href="/index-all">索引</a>
        <a href="/concepts/citation-layer">概念</a>
        <a href="/methodology/why-format-has-ceiling">方法</a>
        <a href="/guides/why-ai-recommends-others">指南</a>
        <a href="/about">关于</a>
      </nav>
    </header>
    <main>
      <slot />
    </main>
    <footer class="site-footer">
      <div class="footer-section">
        <strong>概念</strong>
        <a href="/concepts/search-layer">搜索层</a>
        <a href="/concepts/citation-layer">引用层</a>
        <a href="/concepts/adoption-rate">采纳率</a>
        <a href="/concepts/kindling-and-light">火种与火光</a>
        <a href="/concepts/reasoning-slope">推理坡度</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-section">
        <strong>方法论</strong>
        <a href="/methodology/why-format-has-ceiling">格式优化的天花板</a>
        <a href="/methodology/how-ai-selects-sources">AI如何选择信息源</a>
        <a href="/methodology/visibility-vs-adoption">可见性与采纳率</a>
        <a href="/methodology/content-sovereignty">内容主权与工具主权</a>
        <a href="/methodology/two-readers">两类读者</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-section">
        <strong>证据</strong>
        <a href="/evidence/geo-paper">GEO论文解读</a>
        <a href="/evidence/platform-adoption-test">多平台采纳测试</a>
        <a href="/evidence/baseline-comparison">基线对照实验</a>
        <a href="/evidence/self-attestation">自证特性</a>
        <a href="/evidence/multi-convergence-vs-linear">多维收敛vs线性堆叠</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-section">
        <strong>指南</strong>
        <a href="/guides/why-ai-recommends-others">为什么AI推荐别人不推荐你</a>
        <a href="/guides/ai-vs-search-engine">AI搜索vs传统搜索</a>
        <a href="/guides/how-to-get-cited">怎么让内容被AI引用</a>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-section">
        <strong>站点</strong>
        <a href="/index-all">完整索引</a>
        <a href="/about">关于</a>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>

<style is:global>
  @import '../styles/global.css';
</style>
